high_descs: Walk forward across the room, then turn left and cross the room, then turn left and face the end of the table.
Pick up the knife at the far end of the table.
Turn around and face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Place the knife on top of the sponge.
Pick up a piece of the apple.
Turn to the right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and cross the room, then turn right and cross the room and turn to the right to face the end of the table.
Place the piece of apple on the end of the table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it on the end of the table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the white table below the window.
Pick up the knife, between the salt and the wine bottle, on the table.
Turn around and walk to the small counter to the right of the stove.
Cut the apple in front of the blue bowl, on the counter, into slices.
Place the knife on the green and yellow sponge, on the counter.
Pick up one of the apple slices from the counter.
Move over to your right, so that you are directly in front of the stove and microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the apple slice from the microwave.
Turn to your left and go to the left end of the white table, under the window.
Place the apple slice on the front, left corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the right side of the white table on the left.
Pick up the knife near the wine bottle on the table.
Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Cut the apple into threes.
Place the knife on the green sponge.
Pick up one piece of the cut apple.
Go right to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the apple piece briefly.
Turn around and go to the right side of the white table.
Place the apple piece in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple piece on the table.
